pos_examples: Now, apply the action "drop" to rover yew and store fire.
Once you are done, please apply the action "communicate_image_data" to rover object_260, lander frame_9, objective teddy, mode dress_red, waypoint star_213 and waypoint rain.
(communicate_image_data object_260 frame_9 teddy dress_red star_213 rain)

First, apply the action "communicate_soil_data" to rover yew, lander roof_11, waypoint rain, waypoint rain_45 and waypoint star_213 and then apply the action "calibrate" to rover yew, camera kumquat, objective bastion and waypoint rain_45.

(communicate_soil_data yew roof_11 rain rain_45 star_213)
(calibrate yew kumquat bastion rain_45)
The next step is to apply the action "navigate" to rover yew, waypoint star_213 and waypoint rain_45.
